sg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T17:32:52.000Z","msg":"罷埋聽日好啦 1日或者逐個行業罷真係作用不大 之後着力入黎幫手搞工會同R多d人<br />\n二百萬三罷聯合陣線&nbsp;<a href=\"http://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2LdcWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=d10a5022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\n好多援助同工會先啱啱起步 未成熟 再咁吹風真係會狼來了 同埋令唔少自己友比人炒<br />\n認同set死線有必要 但係行動升級點解只限於罷工<br />\n升級可以係工業區和你lunch 18區裝修 迫商場閂門 都可以影響經濟<br />\n我視大罷工為雙面刃 需做好最大準備 盡量減少對我方傷害 先好實行<br />\n歡迎討論 集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"552fb26fd783107bdbf508589c65f00684dc87c0","tid":1775210,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T17:34:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a6d26e6d15f6eeab5790a436f45b86d514ed41c3","tid":1775210,"uid":154892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T17:36:36.000Z","msg":"但係番工時段裝修會唔會好危<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a188f674348363d7c498f21cdbb262f7e26a9c2b","tid":1775210,"uid":262346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T17:36:45.000Z","msg":"唔好忘記有好多老人院既人<br />\n腥香港人<br />\n同點都唔出黎淺黃藍既星斗市民 <br />\n係真沉默大多數<br />\n<br />\n80萬係好撚多"},{"pid":"e3141d32c35236054c52b53aa7404aded2ce8c4e","tid":1775210,"uid":291802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c29098534607ae611d4aead4305b6c3fd1bc3341","tid":1775210,"uid":202076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T16:52:19.000Z","msg":"關於黎明行動，我覺得可以咁樣轉型<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1775177\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1775177</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T17:41:12.000Z","msg":"Pushhhhhh"},{"pid":"71692f8b9a7e0c7bb8d7b05b1f1cb12dc1cff11d","tid":1775210,"uid":113481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T17:42:11.000Z","msg":"星期二12月10日有Asia Insurance Forum,喺灣仔會展會搞足一日<br />\n啲嘉賓有林鄭、大陸銀保監會、國際間做有關保險嘅官員、大粒嘢<br />\n保險業幫香港賺好多錢、佔GDP好多，係非常之大嘅一個春袋<br />\n大家記住去支持下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊塞爆會展<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e3c98b8ff6f1ac0b42c5e6176d5714524457ff","tid":1775210,"uid":108450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T17:44:10.000Z","msg":"我一路都有好撚大個問題。 真勇武日日玩旺角黑夜 尖沙咀黑夜 得返堆無戰鬥力既學生 半和理非塞鐵 唔比人拉就有鬼啦。。<br />\n<br />\n要影響經濟最簡單 咪就係商場 鋪頭落閘 咁自然全世界自動罷工啦 。 其實兩三個火魔落地我諗 三條街內啲鋪頭餐廳銀行乜春都閂曬啦<br />\n<br />\n小隊 地下 遊擊 快閃"}]}